snippet.title: CIPHER 8 [Steam Trailer]
snippet.description:
CIPHER 8 on Steam: https://store.steampowered.com/app/2552900/CIPHER8/
CIPHER-8 is coming to Steam on September 12, 2023 as a FREE game to celebrate 8 years of PICO-8, the coziest virtual fantasy console out there!

Gameplay: https://youtu.be/f1Hi7kevwq0
https://www.fischergamedesign.com/
